{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775880761744,"sessionID":"ses_285427d8effefV7BefOfDq6hUq","part":{"id":"prt_d7abdec55001KiRt04Teh5m6wx","messageID":"msg_d7abde115001SIhnwEH9XSPaPK","sessionID":"ses_285427d8effefV7BefOfDq6hUq","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_b0abad6c1ca443999fcebc93","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-037/delta-spec.md","limit":80},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-037/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-037: PCAP 分析器示例应用 - Delta Specification\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the PCAP analyzer example application in the AgentCube `example` module.\n6: \n7: ## Base Specifications\n8: \n9: - **AR**: AR-037\n10: - **Module**: `example`\n11: - **Language**: Python\n12: - **Size**: M\n13: - **Reference Sources**: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/example/pcap-analyzer/`, `python-sdk/design.md`, `python-sdk/spec.md`\n14: \n15: ---\n16: \n17: ## Files to Add\n18: \n19: | Path | Description | Type |\n20: |------|-------------|------|\n21: | `example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` | FastAPI application with SandboxRunner, ReActAgent, Planner, and Reporter | New |\n22: | `example/pcap-analyzer/requirements.txt` | Dependencies: fastapi, uvicorn, langchain-openai, scapy | New |\n23: | `example/pcap-analyzer/Dockerfile` | Container image definition | New |\n24: | `example/pcap-analyzer/deployment.yaml` | Kubernetes deployment manifest | New |\n25: | `example/pcap-analyzer/README.md` | Usage documentation | New |\n26: \n27: ---\n28: \n29: ## Files to Modify\n30: \n31: | Path | Description | Change Type |\n32: |------|-------------|-------------|\n33: | | | |\n34: \n35: ---\n36: \n37: ## Files to Delete\n38: \n39: | Path | Description |\n40: |------|-------------|\n41: | | |\n42: \n43: ---\n44: \n45: ## Requirements\n46: \n47: ### AR-037-001: PCAP Analyzer Module Structure\n48: \n49: The system SHALL provide a complete `example/pcap-analyzer/` module demonstrating AgentCube SDK usage.\n50: \n51: #### Scenario: AR-037-001-A — Module directory exists\n52: \n53: - **GIVEN** the workspace root at `example/`\n54: - **WHEN** the directory is inspected\n55: - **THEN** it SHALL contain `pcap-analyzer/` subdirectory with all required files\n56: \n57: #### Scenario: AR-037-001-B — Required files present\n58: \n59: - **GIVEN** `example/pcap-analyzer/` directory\n60: - **WHEN** files are listed\n61: - **THEN** it SHALL contain `pcap_analyzer.py`, `requirements.txt`, `Dockerfile`, `deployment.yaml`, and `README.md`\n62: \n63: ---\n64: \n65: ### AR-037-002: PCAP Analyzer FastAPI Application\n66: \n67: The system SHALL provide a FastAPI application that orchestrates PCAP analysis.\n68: \n69: #### Scenario: AR-037-002-A — Application startup with API key\n70: \n71: - **GIVEN** `pcap_analyzer.py` is started with valid `OPENAI_API_KEY` environment variable\n72: - **WHEN** the application completes startup hooks\n73: - **THEN** it SHALL initialize LLM client, PLANNER agent, and REPORTER agent\n74: - **AND** bind to `0.0.0.0:8000`\n75: \n76: #### Scenario: AR-037-002-B — Application startup without API key\n77: \n78: - **GIVEN** `pcap_analyzer.py` is started without a valid `OPENAI_API_KEY`\n79: - **WHEN** the application attempts startup\n80: - **THEN** startup SHALL fail with an error rather than serve requests\n\n(Showing lines 1-80 of 389. Use offset=81 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-037: PCAP 分析器示例应用 - Delta Specification\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the PCAP analyzer example application in the AgentCube `example` module.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-037\n- **Module**: `example`\n- **Language**: Python\n- **Size**: M\n- **Reference Sources**: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/example/pcap-analyzer/`, `python-sdk/design.md`, `python-sdk/spec.md`\n\n---\n\n## Files to Add\n\n| Path | Description | Type |\n|------|-------------|------|","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-037/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775880761713,"end":1775880761742}}}}
