{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775880796703,"sessionID":"ses_285427d8effefV7BefOfDq6hUq","part":{"id":"prt_d7abe5e3f001RIlbIG3fPoDKlT","messageID":"msg_d7abe536f001Ohs5uesoYtK6QM","sessionID":"ses_285427d8effefV7BefOfDq6hUq","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_c8c61a601c2b443082216d3b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-038: Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n\n## Summary\n\n为 AgentCube 项目的 workloadmanager 模块编写全面的 Go 单元测试，提高代码质量和可维护性。\n\n---\n\n## Purpose\n\n### Background\n\nworkloadmanager 模块是 AgentCube 的核心组件，负责工作负载管理、调度和生命周期管理。当前该模块已有部分测试，但覆盖率和测试深度有待提升。\n\n### Goal\n\n1. 为 workloadmanager 模块编写全面的单元测试\n2. 提高测试覆盖率到目标水平\n3. 确保关键业务逻辑的测试覆盖\n4. 建立持续测试的基础设施\n\n### Value\n\n- 提高代码质量，减少 regression\n- 为重构提供安全网\n- 提高开发者信心\n- 满足质量门禁要求\n\n---\n\n## Scope\n\n### In-Scope\n\n- pkg/workloadmanager 下的所有业务逻辑测试\n- 关键路径的单元测试\n- 边界条件和错误处理测试\n\n### Out-of-Scope\n\n- 集成测试\n- 性能测试\n- E2E 测试\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n1. 单元测试通过率 100%\n2. 测试覆盖率目标 ≥ 70%\n3. 所有关键业务逻辑都有对应的测试用例\n4. 测试代码符合 Go 最佳实践","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775880796694,"end":1775880796701}}}}
