{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775880805387,"sessionID":"ses_285427d8effefV7BefOfDq6hUq","part":{"id":"prt_d7abe87110015L0GNiIShjZo4b","messageID":"msg_d7abe7a4d001oSLkcZyMFbQJvn","sessionID":"ses_285427d8effefV7BefOfDq6hUq","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_58b687db954d46d7a9d22e42","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-038: Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager) - Tasks\n\n## Task List\n\n- [ ] 1. 分析现有测试覆盖情况\n- [ ] 2. 识别需要测试的核心模块和函数\n- [ ] 3. 编写 service 层测试\n- [ ] 4. 编写 reconciler 测试\n- [ ] 5. 编写 client 测试\n- [ ] 6. 编写 types 测试\n- [ ] 7. 补充边缘情况和错误处理测试\n- [ ] 8. 运行测试并修复失败用例\n- [ ] 9. 验证测试覆盖率\n- [ ] 10. 代码审查和优化\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Go 1.21+\n- testing package (stdlib)\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\nSize: L - Large change requiring comprehensive testing across multiple modules.","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-038/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-038/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-038/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775880805370,"end":1775880805384}}}}
